S'imaginescha egna pagina-web fetg lùnga cun egna massa secziùns (peia egna specificaziùn HTML sen egna pagina). Sch'igl utilisader dumonda egna tschearta secziùn (p.ex. page.html#section7) , co fuss igl, sch'igl server-web streams gl'amprem quella secziùn a suainter tschellas secziùns?
Streaming order:
1. antscheata digl documaint HTML antocen <body>
2. HTML per secziun 7
3. HTML par secziùns 1, 2, 3 etc.
Alura procurass igl navigatur ca las partiziùns 1 antocen 6 *davart* la partiziùn 7 vignan mussadas sen la pagina-web.
Fa quegl sen? Fuss quegl gidevel?
La secziùn culiada (#section7) duess vagnir renderada aschi speart sco pussevel sainza stuer implementar danovameing elemaints cun JavaScript. Jou less semplameing ver egn documaint HTML extralùng, mo igls tschancùns culiieus den vagnir renderos aschi speart sco pussevel. Cun HTML duess quegl funcziunar.
Igl cuntegn savess ascheia vagnir strimo, ad alura matess igl navigatur tut igls <contents> an la <div>.
< div id = sec1></div>
< div id= sec2></div>
etc.
< div id = sec7>section 7...</div>
< contents for=sec1>section 1...</contents>
< contents for=sec2>section 2...</contents>
etc.
Igl vagness betga streamo an roda, mo igl navigatur matess anzemel igl documaint HTML sco sch'igl fuss vagnieu streamo an roda.
